Subject: [PATCH 5/5] install/block: include vmd module

The vmd module may allow to use the disk on some systems that use the Intel Volume Management Device technology.

Fixes https://bugs.archlinux.org/task/68704 .
---
 install/block | 3 +++
 1 file changed, 3 insertions(+)

diff --git a/install/block b/install/block
index 98ea509..20eb7cb 100644
--- a/install/block
+++ b/install/block
@@ -26,6 +26,9 @@ build() {
 
     # nvdimm
     add_checked_modules '/drivers/nvdimm/'
+
+    # Intel Volume Management Device
+    add_checked_modules 'vmd'
 }
 
 help() {
